1
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:41,120
You should recognize this shipping manifest.

2
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:49,959
This manifest contains

3
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:51,719
3 months of herb transfer records between

4
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:55,000
Green Wood Hall and Mystic Water Hall.

5
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:58,120
Including this batch of tainted auxiliary herbs,

6
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:00,680
handled by Lu Ning from Mystic Water Hall,

7
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,599
and delivered to Misty Herb Sanctuary.

8
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,439
This manifest alone?

9
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:14,080
What does this manifest prove?

10
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,319
At most, it only proves

11
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:17,560
that Mystic Water Hall handled the transport.

12
00:02:18,439 --> 00:02:19,759
As for what you claim,

13
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,919
that I swapped the tainted herbs,

14
00:02:22,479 --> 00:02:24,400
on what grounds do you frame me without evidence?

15
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,400
Besides,

16
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:29,439
Mystic Water Hall's herb transport

17
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:31,560
has always been extremely rigorous.

18
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:35,319
That person you mentioned, this Lu Ning,

19
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,199
Sorry to disappoint you,

20
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:37,479
but in our Mystic Water Hall,

21
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:38,560
no such person exists.

22
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,319
Medicine Master Lu,

23
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:47,120
you really won't quit until you hit a wall.

24
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,199
Li Mouren,

25
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,439
I, Ye Qingxue,

26
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,759
never fight a battle unprepared.

27
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:05,879
Xiao Qiu,

28
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,719
Are they bringing him up already?

29
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:15,080
She's about to reveal the truth right here!

30
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,479
Keep moving!

31
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:18,879
How is Mystic Water Hall so well-prepared?

32
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:23,000
If you ask me, Lu Daozai was thoroughly investigated in secret.

33
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:23,840
Keep moving!

34
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,560
That's him!

35
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,159
Lu Ning,

36
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:28,199
have you seen him before?

37
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:29,039
Never seen him.

38
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:37,159
Lu Ning.

39
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:41,319
You're the one in charge of herb transport for Mystic Water Hall, right?

40
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,240
That's me.

41
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:50,639
But I only handle transport.

42
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,520
I don't know about anything else.

43
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:56,120
Those herbs were...

44
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,719
It was Lu Daozai.

45
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,680
He arranged for someone to swap them.

46
00:04:05,199 --> 00:04:06,039
What nonsense!

47
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:06,840
I don't even know you.

48
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,719
Medicine Master Lu.

49
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:10,400
How can you just pretend not to know me?

50
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,960
I've been risking my life for you!

51
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,879
I see how it is.

52
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,039
You're all conspiring to frame me.

53
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:15,560
Isn't that right?

54
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:18,720
I have proof.

55
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:21,040
All the evidence is right here.

56
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:28,040
You backstabbing little wretch!

57
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:29,879
Move!

58
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:31,480
Don't touch me!

59
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:33,879
Medicine Master Lu!

60
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,160
Let go!

61
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,519
Don't touch me!

62
00:04:43,079 --> 00:04:44,759
Magnificent.

63
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:45,480
Medicine Master Lu.

64
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:48,439
Mystic Medicine Association's reputation,

65
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:50,079
you nearly destroyed it.

66
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:50,680
Enough.

67
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:53,040
Medicine Master Li.

68
00:04:55,319 --> 00:04:55,639
Medicine Master Li.

69
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:58,800
Lu Daozai is still a Medicine Master of our association.

70
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,680
Take him away.

71
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,800
We'll discuss this later.

72
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:03,079
He's done for.

73
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:04,839
Just dragged off like that.

74
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:05,839
I don't know anything!

75
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:06,839
Well done. Now scram.

76
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:09,319
This year's Medical Trial is anything but peaceful.

77
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:10,560
Unbelievable.

78
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,519
Medicine Master Lu has been caught.

79
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:17,120
But who knows...

80
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:19,399
if there's anyone else behind him pulling the strings.

81
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,759
Miss Ye.

82
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:25,839
The Medical Trial matters most right now.

83
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:28,079
We mustn't miss the appointed hour.

84
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,399
Or we won't make it into the Heart-Questioning Realm.

85
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,040
Don't worry.

86
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,120
You've got me.

87
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:43,759
The evidence against Lu Daozai is solid.

88
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:46,759
After the Trial, we'll investigate thoroughly.

89
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:48,000
And give everyone the truth.

90
00:05:49,879 --> 00:05:51,560
You and Yunfan can rest easy.

91
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:56,000
Okay.

92
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:01,439
According to the Medical Trial rules,

93
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,360
in this round,

94
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:05,680
only Li Xiangyang's team treated the patient.

95
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:08,240
They greatly eased his suffering,

96
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,720
and stabilized the condition.

97
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,560
However, his teammate Ye Qingxue

98
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,600
did not participate in the treatment.

99
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,600
Therefore,

100
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,439
only Li Xiangyang advances.

101
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,879
What about me?

102
00:06:23,879 --> 00:06:25,399
I treated the patient too!

103
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:28,839
Yang Yunfan, you have no shame!

104
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,240
Everyone saw it.

105
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:33,120
The patient coughed up blood after taking your medicine.

106
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,399
The fact that he's still alive

107
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:36,759
is a miracle in itself, okay?

108
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:42,199
He looks fine.

109
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:42,959
What's going on?

110
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:43,800
He seems to have recovered.

111
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:45,639
I think so too.

112
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,160
Yang Yunfan is really impressive.

113
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:50,040
Truly remarkable.

114
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,040
You couldn't tell at all just now.

115
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:51,680
So impressive.

116
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,639
Right?

117
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:54,839
Are you feeling better?

118
00:06:57,639 --> 00:06:59,439
The Extreme Yin condition is fully healed.

119
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:02,120
Your Malevolent Qi is completely cleansed.

120
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:13,439
This technique

121
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:17,000
took me a lifetime of effort to create.

122
00:07:17,639 --> 00:07:20,120
It can temporarily suppress Malevolent Qi.

123
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:31,160
Today, I'll pass this method on to you.

124
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:34,879
With your aptitude,

125
00:07:34,879 --> 00:07:35,680
I'm sure you'll master it.

126
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,959
Father, this is impossible.

127
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:57,560
This must be a trap they set up.

128
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:04,839
Medicine Master Li.

129
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:10,199
Since the patient has fully recovered,

130
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:12,920
shouldn't Young Master Yang's eligibility

131
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,920
be restored and his promotion granted?

132
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,399
Fine.

133
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:23,959
Yang Yunfan,

134
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,000
you advance.

135
00:08:28,959 --> 00:08:31,519
From now on, in the Association,

136
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:33,039
you shall serve as a Medicine Master.

137
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,000
Both of you, prepare yourselves.

138
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,120
Get ready to enter the Heart-Questioning Realm.

139
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,399
Thank you, Medicine Master Li.

140
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:44,360
So next time we meet, we'll be peers, right?

141
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,519
How was that?

142
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:52,080
Wasn't I impressive just now?

143
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:54,120
Impressive.

144
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,279
But...

145
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,879
the Heart-Questioning Realm is perilous.

146
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:58,960
Li Mouren will never let this go.

147
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,399
Ye Qingxue,

148
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,960
I just got promoted to Medicine Master,

149
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:06,120
and you don't even bother to encourage me?

150
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,360
You still want me to keep taking the trial?

151
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,320
Do you have a heart or what?

152
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,519
As a newly promoted Medicine Master,

153
00:09:12,519 --> 00:09:14,080
how can you possibly stand against him?

154
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,960
He has led Red Fire Hall and run the

155
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,399
Mystic Medicine Association for years.

156
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:24,080
What does that have to do with the Heart-Questioning Realm?

157
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:27,399
If you can pass

158
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:29,240
the trial of the Heart-Questioning Realm,

159
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:33,519
you can qualify to be the Medicine Heir.

160
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:35,600
That would make you

161
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,759
second only to the Medicine Venerable.

162
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:40,039
Your status would outrank Li Mouren's,

163
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,720
and that's how you can take him down.

164
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:43,840
I didn't quite catch all that,

165
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:46,639
but this "Medicine Heir" sounds familiar.

166
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,279
Your father,

167
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,440
Yang Mingyuan was the Medicine Heir then.

168
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,559
But aside from Uncle Yang,

169
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:57,720
no one has passed the trial in years.

170
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:04,519
If my dad was that incredible,

171
00:10:04,519 --> 00:10:05,960
how bad could his son possibly be?

172
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,399
I believe in you.

173
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:13,159
But the Heart-Questioning Realm is truly dangerous.

174
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:16,840
You must face your deepest fears and desires.

175
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,559
You must hold true to your heart

176
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:20,240
to break through the illusions and demons.

177
00:10:21,279 --> 00:10:22,919
After Uncle Yang passed,

178
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:24,000
for all these years,

179
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,360
many Medicine Masters tried multiple times,

180
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,399
and none succeeded.

181
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,279
It's truly dangerous.

182
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:31,720
Alright.

183
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,840
Your most important task right now

184
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,240
is to rest and recover.

185
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,399
You know perfectly well how amazing I am.

186
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:39,759
Besides,

187
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:41,000
from now on,

188
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:44,000
don't call me "Yunfan" in front of others.

189
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,440
Now I am

190
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,559
Medicine Master Yang.

191
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,720
Okay.

192
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,159
Medicine Master Yang,

193
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,000
you'd better get going.

194
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:57,720
I'm off.

195
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,799
I'll wait for your return.

196
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,120
What about Lin Hongxiu?

197
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,159
With assassins from Hequan Pharmaceuticals,

198
00:11:28,159 --> 00:11:29,399
we've already caught her.

199
00:11:29,399 --> 00:11:30,159
She's locked up at Wujie now.

200
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,279
Keep her alive for now.

201
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:34,559
She's still useful.

202
00:11:34,559 --> 00:11:35,000
Yes, sir.

203
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:49,480
Yang Yunfan's hiding more than I thought.

204
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:51,200
I suspect

205
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,679
that before Yang Mingyuan died,

206
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:54,960
he likely passed the Primordial Purple Qi Art

207
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,600
to him in secret.

208
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:57,440
How could that be?

209
00:11:58,399 --> 00:12:00,279
That's the Medicine Venerable's ultimate art.

210
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:02,320
Even Yang Mingyuan couldn't learn it so fast.

211
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:06,960
Yang Mingyuan was the Medicine Heir back then,

212
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,360
groomed by the Medicine Venerable himself.

213
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,720
He'd long surpassed ordinary people.

214
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:13,279
Yang Yunfan must not stand in your way.

215
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,720
If you fail to get the Primordial Purple Qi Art,

216
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:19,000
I'll take him out at once myself.

217
00:12:27,799 --> 00:12:29,799
This is your last chance to be cured.

218
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:31,320
Xiangyang,

219
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:35,559
I will absolutely not let

220
00:12:35,559 --> 00:12:36,559
anything happen to you.

221
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,279
For such a grand occasion today,

222
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:34,519
you'd think they'd bring an audience to liven things up.

223
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:36,159
It feels a bit deserted, doesn't it?

224
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,799
The Heart-Questioning Realm

225
00:13:38,799 --> 00:13:40,759
is the Association's most sacred place.

226
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,320
It is never revealed to outsiders.

227
00:13:43,039 --> 00:13:44,600
For the two of you today

228
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:47,120
to enter together via the Medical Trial

229
00:13:47,679 --> 00:13:49,159
is already an exception.

230
00:13:49,159 --> 00:13:50,559
You should be grateful.

231
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:52,840
What's wrong?

232
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,519
Yang Yunfan,

233
00:13:54,279 --> 00:13:55,879
with no one to back you up,

234
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:56,639
are you scared now?

235
00:13:57,320 --> 00:14:00,320
A loser like you should stop yapping.

236
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:02,080
You think relying on your father

237
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:04,159
will let you turn things around here?

238
00:14:04,799 --> 00:14:06,320
I'll still make you lose everything.

239
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:07,679
Enough.

240
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:11,799
Since you're both ready,

241
00:14:11,799 --> 00:14:13,000
go on inside, quickly.

242
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,080
Don't waste time out here.

243
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,720
Just wait.

244
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:17,320
Yang Yunfan,

245
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:20,200
you'll definitely regret

246
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,799
every word you said today.

247
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,519
I bet you'll cry before I do.
